<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>The Bachelor's Locky Gilbert was set to visit the families of the remaining women vying for his heart.</p>

<p>But on Wednesday, he was unable to meet frontrunner Irena Srbinovska's loved ones as Melbourne border closures prevented them travelling to Sydney.</p>

<p>After host Osher Günsberg delivered the news to Locky, 30, and Irena, 31, fans rushed to social media to channel The Bachelor's relief.   </p>

<p>'No face to face': On Wednesday, Locky Gilbert was unable to meet rumoured winner Irena Srbinovska's family during home visits on The Bachelor - and fans took to Twitter to share his relief</p>

<p>'Locky is like, thank f*** I don't have to meet her parents in person,' one fan wrote on Twitter. </p>

<p>Another viewer shared an image of a man smiling and wrote: 'Locky finding out he doesn't actually have to meet the family in person.' </p>

<p> 'Locky is ABSOLUTELY delighted that he does not have to meet Irena's family let's be real,' quipped another.</p>

<p>Before a fourth swiftly got down to brass tacks. 'Bet Locky is relieved he doesn't have to see the protective brother face to face,' the wrote.  </p>

<p>Phew! After host Osher Günsberg delivered the news to Locky, 30, and Irena, 31, fans rushed to social media to channel The Bachelor's relief.</p>

<p>'Secretly happy': On Twitter one wrote, 'Locky is like, thank f*** I don't have to meet her parents in person'</p>

<p>During the episode, Osher surprised Locky and Irena during their hiking date to break the sad news. </p>

<p>He explained that the COVID situation in Melbourne had worsened since she returned to the mansion and that Melbourne was under lockdown again and that the border between New South Wales and Victoria was shut. </p>

<p>'Irena, I'm so sorry but your family was not able to make it today,' Osher said as Irena hugged Locky.  </p>

<p>Bad news: During the episode, Osher surprised Locky and Irena during their hiking date to break the sad news</p>

<p>Relief: 'Bet Locky is relieved he doesn't have to see the protective brother face to face,' wrote one fan</p>

<p>Plan B: They were instead forced to meet over a video call. Pictured, right: Irena's father Vasco, mother Vesna and brother Igor</p>

<p>'You're not gonna be able to see them face-to-face, however, thankfully, the internet still exists, we have arranged for a videocall,' he revealed.</p>

<p>On Wednesday night, Izzy Sharman-Firth and intruder Bec Cvilikas failed to get a rose from Locky, leaving Irena and Bella Varelis as the final two.</p>

<p>The Bachelor finale airs Thursday at 7.30pm on Channel 10 </p>

<p>Bye now: On Wednesday night, Izzy Sharman-Firth (left) and intruder Bec Cvilikas (right) failed to get a rose from Locky. The Bachelor finale airs Thursday at 7.30pm on Channel 10</p>
